	<div class="pane" id="step1">
		<p>Country Commercial Guides (CCGs) are present a comprehensive look at countries' commercial environments, using economic, political and market analysis. The CCGs were established by recommendation of the Trade Promotion Coordinating Committee (TPCC), a multi-agency task force, to consolidate various reporting documents prepared for the U.S. business community.</p>
		<p>The Country Commercial Guides API breaks down the large report into searchable sections for countries of Argentina, Brazil, Colombia, China, and Panama.</p>
		<p>The output format for this API is JSON.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="pane" id="step2">
		<p>The Country Commercial Guides offer valuable content about an exporting market, but the content was only currently available in via a formatted document.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="pane" id="step3">
		<p>Sections of the Country Commercial Guides appeal to different types of business users, so you may target specific types of content to the right audience. 
		</p>
	</div>

